  "detailed_description": "<h1>Muffed is Better with Gamepads!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/f48ef322d7620bf1c296860ef6f2f612.avif?t=1761001279\" width=600 height=160 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/ab89737202472aaca35ccc223b196f05.avif?t=1761001279\" width=600 height=244 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/39286235090fbc966cc3e8c10200947d.poster.avif?t=1761001279\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/39286235090fbc966cc3e8c10200947d.webm?t=1761001279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/39286235090fbc966cc3e8c10200947d.mp4?t=1761001279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Send someone home crying with 9 Battle Modes, 15 maps, and split screen for up to 16 players!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Nobody has to watch, your friends can play too.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/ffa1a000cc235114376ecbdc96781c4c.avif?t=1761001279\" width=600 height=244 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/43e13965dd1e71b822223537a19a5b45.poster.avif?t=1761001279\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/43e13965dd1e71b822223537a19a5b45.webm?t=1761001279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/43e13965dd1e71b822223537a19a5b45.mp4?t=1761001279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Hunt Dr. Wolfe down (with up to 3 friends) across 25 levels and 5 boss battles in the Co-Op campaign</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/63360648ae767638d75a271eb8f087a6.poster.avif?t=1761001279\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/63360648ae767638d75a271eb8f087a6.webm?t=1761001279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/63360648ae767638d75a271eb8f087a6.mp4?t=1761001279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Finished the campaign? Test your mettle in the 4 endless survival levels, definitely co-opable</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/8fc753a92ba07bcf8363317954c9fb97.avif?t=1761001279\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Not vibing with these levels? Make your own and share with the community in the Workshop</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/b83cdbe892ac6a10d5f861e6495f33e6.poster.avif?t=1761001279\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/b83cdbe892ac6a10d5f861e6495f33e6.webm?t=1761001279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Awesome Muffs headphones provide extra slaying power  (batteries not included)</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/9fdd3b58122857b7cedc8f0607aafbd7.poster.avif?t=1761001279\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/9fdd3b58122857b7cedc8f0607aafbd7.webm?t=1761001279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/9fdd3b58122857b7cedc8f0607aafbd7.mp4?t=1761001279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Over 50 weapons so you can play your way, or just throw stuff, no judgement here</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/165aa2fd7935335a93dc95ab6392439b.poster.avif?t=1761001279\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/165aa2fd7935335a93dc95ab6392439b.webm?t=1761001279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/165aa2fd7935335a93dc95ab6392439b.mp4?t=1761001279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Holiday Theming—because it's not a holiday party unless it ends in a fight</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Happy Hunting!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661200/extras/af8a7fb9ecc8c752d023d9899da2ac9a.avif?t=1761001279\" width=150 height=128 /></span><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Kelsam</strong></p>",
